                </p>
                <ul className="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Pay {entryFee} ETH entry fee</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Fund your smart account</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Mirror trades automatically</li>
